node.text: This week for your chance to win a $250 Erin Condren gift card, we want to see your daily planner spreads! Don’t worry, you don’t have to have our Daily Duo Planner to enter- just show us each day in your LifePlanner™. Post your Instagram Reel or Tiktok with your daily spreads for your chance to win! Each week 3 lucky winners can win a $250 EC gift card and be featured on our page. (link in our bio for more rules) #lifewithEC and #erincondren. Make sure you're following us here or on TikTok @ erincondrendesign for your chance to win! #giveaway #planneraddict #plannerinspiration #plannercommunity
